    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good overall condition and has been consistently maintained to ensure reliability. The engine starts easily and runs smoothly, making it an excellent choice for a daily driver. While the exterior is clean and well-preserved, there are a few minor cosmetic blemishes consistent with regular use. The interior is tidy and comfortable, showing only light wear on the upholstery. Overall, it is a solid, dependable car that is ready for the road.",
      "price": 34500.0,
